A prominent politician is counting double losses. The man, who has been supporting the flashy lifestyle of a city slay queen, was left in shock after she was sponsored for a trip to Dubai by another man. According to our source, the damsel, keen to keep her clandestine affairs private, went on to block him from viewing her status updates. As if that is not enough, the couple are not friends on social media, hence the politician has to settle for the little the damsel left behind. The politician also doubles up as a pimp for female friends brought along by his girlfriend. According to a close friend o the politician, he keeps his affair low key and only interacts with people who will not betray him. The damsel seems to be making hay while the sun shines, given that the politician is not the only moneybag in her life.